Package com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.reasoner.model

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Definition
    Interface for definitions that can provide class expressions and axioms to a concept definition.
    DefinitionNodeKey
    Interface for definition node keys that can provide class expressions and axioms to a concept definition.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnnotatedDefinition
    Common superclass for ConceptDefinitions and RelationshipDefinitions, providing additional ConcreteDomainDefinitions to their general ontology descriptions.
    ConceptDefinition
    Aggregates relationships and concrete domain entries that together form the definition of a concept.
    ConceptDefinitionBuilder
    Utility class for generating ConceptDefinition from a Concept instance.
    ConcreteDomainDefinition
    Represents a short version of a concrete domain reference set member for ontology definitions.
    DefinitionNode
    Represents a composite node of the definition which carries a set of RelationshipDefinitions as well as optional sub-DefinitionNodes.
    LongConcepts
    A SNOMED CT concept ID collection which holds constants in primitive long form.
    Node
    Represents the root node of the concept definition, capable of storing sub-nodes keyed by DefinitionNodeKeys.
    NonZeroGroupKey
    A DefinitionNodeKey implementation collecting OWL definitions for "regular" relationship groups.
    RelationshipDefinition
    Represents a short form of SNOMED CT relationships for use in OWL ontology axioms.
    RoleInclusionKey
    A DefinitionNodeKey implementation for role inclusion nodes.
    SnomedOntologyUtils
    Utility class that holds OWL object identifier prefixes as well as methods for creating class expressions for object intersections and unions.
    UnionGroupKey
    A DefinitionNodeKey implementation collecting OWL definitions for union groups (both in never grouped relationships and in groups).
    WritableEmptySet<E>
    A Set implementation which is backed by a shared empty set until a write operation is invoked; this replaces the empty, read-only delegate with a writable HashSet.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    IsaKey
    Singleton node key for the definition node storing ISA relationships only.
    NeverGroupedKey
    A singleton DefinitionNodeKey implementation collecting OWL definitions for never grouped relationships.
    ZeroGroupKey
    A DefinitionNodeKey implementation collecting OWL definitions for "regular" relationship groups with group number 0.
